powerpc64/bpf elfv1: Do not load TOC before calling functions

jira LE-1907
Rebuild_History Non-Buildable kernel-4.18.0-481.el8
commit-author Naveen N. Rao <naveen.n.rao@linux.vnet.ibm.com>
